                </li>
                <li class="flex items-center gap-2 text-body-sm text-brand-gray">
                  <Icon name="check-circle" size="sm" class="text-brand-orange flex-shrink-0" />
                  Air quality testing if needed
                </li>
              </ul>
            </div>
          </div>
        </div>
        
        <!-- Step 2 -->
        <div class="bg-white rounded-xl p-6 shadow-card">
          <div class="flex items-start gap-4">
            <div class="flex-shrink-0 w-14 h-14 rounded-xl bg-brand-orange text-white flex items-center justify-center font-display text-2xl">
              2
            </div>
            <div>
              <h3 class="font-heading font-bold text-display-sm text-brand-black mb-2">Containment & Protection</h3>
              <p class="text-brand-gray mb-4">
                Before any removal begins, we establish containment barriers using plastic sheeting and negative air pressure to prevent mold spores from spreading to unaffected areas of your home.
              </p>
              <ul class="space-y-2">
                <li class="flex items-center gap-2 text-body-sm text-brand-gray">
                  <Icon name="check-circle" size="sm" class="text-brand-orange flex-shrink-0" />
                  Plastic containment barriers
                </li>
                <li class="flex items-center gap-2 text-body-sm text-brand-gray">
                  <Icon name="check-circle" size="sm" class="text-brand-orange flex-shrink-0" />
                  Negative air pressure systems
                </li>
                <li class="flex items-center gap-2 text-body-sm text-brand-gray">
                  <Icon name="check-circle" size="sm" class="text-brand-orange flex-shrink-0" />
                  HVAC isolation
                </li>
              </ul>
            </div>
          </div>
        </div>
        
        <!-- Step 3 -->
        <div class="bg-white rounded-xl p-6 shadow-card">
          <div class="flex items-start gap-4">
            <div class="flex-shrink-0 w-14 h-14 rounded-xl bg-brand-orange text-white flex items-center justify-center font-display text-2xl">
              3
            </div>
            <div>
              <h3 class="font-heading font-bold text-display-sm text-brand-black mb-2">Air Filtration</h3>
              <p class="text-brand-gray mb-4">
                Throughout the remediation process, we run industrial HEPA air scrubbers to capture airborne mold spores, protecting both our team and your family while we work.
              </p>
              <ul class="space-y-2">
                <li class="flex items-center gap-2 text-body-sm text-brand-gray">
                  <Icon name="check-circle" size="sm" class="text-brand-orange flex-shrink-0" />
                  HEPA air scrubbers
                </li>
                <li class="flex items-center gap-2 text-body-sm text-brand-gray">
                  <Icon name="check-circle" size="sm" class="text-brand-orange flex-shrink-0" />
                  Negative air machines
                </li>
                <li class="flex items-center gap-2 text-body-sm text-brand-gray">
                  <Icon name="check-circle" size="sm" class="text-brand-orange flex-shrink-0" />
                  Continuous air quality monitoring
                </li>
              </ul>
            </div>
          </div>
        </div>
        
        <!-- Step 4 -->
        <div class="bg-white rounded-xl p-6 shadow-card">
          <div class="flex items-start gap-4">
            <div class="flex-shrink-0 w-14 h-14 rounded-xl bg-brand-orange text-white flex items-center justify-center font-display text-2xl">
              4
            </div>
            <div>
              <h3 class="font-heading font-bold text-display-sm text-brand-black mb-2">Mold Removal</h3>
              <p class="text-brand-gray mb-4">
                Our technicians safely remove all mold-contaminated materials. Porous materials like drywall and insulation are removed and disposed of properly, while non-porous surfaces are treated and cleaned.
              </p>
              <ul class="space-y-2">
                <li class="flex items-center gap-2 text-body-sm text-brand-gray">
                  <Icon name="check-circle" size="sm" class="text-brand-orange flex-shrink-0" />
                  Safe removal of contaminated materials
                </li>
                <li class="flex items-center gap-2 text-body-sm text-brand-gray">
                  <Icon name="check-circle" size="sm" class="text-brand-orange flex-shrink-0" />
                  Proper disposal protocols
                </li>
                <li class="flex items-center gap-2 text-body-sm text-brand-gray">
                  <Icon name="check-circle" size="sm" class="text-brand-orange flex-shrink-0" />
                  Surface treatment & cleaning
                </li>
              </ul>
            </div>
          </div>
        </div>
        
        <!-- Step 5 -->
        <div class="bg-white rounded-xl p-6 shadow-card">
          <div class="flex items-start gap-4">
            <div class="flex-shrink-0 w-14 h-14 rounded-xl bg-brand-orange text-white flex items-center justify-center font-display text-2xl">
              5
            </div>
            <div>
              <h3 class="font-heading font-bold text-display-sm text-brand-black mb-2">Cleaning & Treatment</h3>
              <p class="text-brand-gray mb-4">
                All affected areas are thoroughly cleaned with antimicrobial solutions. We treat structural materials to kill remaining spores and prevent future mold growth.
              </p>
              <ul class="space-y-2">
                <li class="flex items-center gap-2 text-body-sm text-brand-gray">
                  <Icon name="check-circle" size="sm" class="text-brand-orange flex-shrink-0" />
                  Antimicrobial application
                </li>
                <li class="flex items-center gap-2 text-body-sm text-brand-gray">
                  <Icon name="check-circle" size="sm" class="text-brand-orange flex-shrink-0" />
                  HEPA vacuuming all surfaces
                </li>
                <li class="flex items-center gap-2 text-body-sm text-brand-gray">
                  <Icon name="check-circle" size="sm" class="text-brand-orange flex-shrink-0" />
                  Encapsulation where appropriate
                </li>
              </ul>
            </div>
          </div>
        </div>
        
        <!-- Step 6 -->
        <div class="bg-white rounded-xl p-6 shadow-card">
          <div class="flex items-start gap-4">
            <div class="flex-shrink-0 w-14 h-14 rounded-xl bg-brand-orange text-white flex items-center justify-center font-display text-2xl">
              6
            </div>
            <div>
              <h3 class="font-heading font-bold text-display-sm text-brand-black mb-2">Restoration & Prevention</h3>
              <p class="text-brand-gray mb-4">
                We repair and restore affected areas—drywall, flooring, painting—and address the moisture source to prevent mold from returning. You get a complete solution, not just a temporary fix.
              </p>
              <ul class="space-y-2">
                <li class="flex items-center gap-2 text-body-sm text-brand-gray">
                  <Icon name="check-circle" size="sm" class="text-brand-orange flex-shrink-0" />
                  Structural repairs
                </li>
                <li class="flex items-center gap-2 text-body-sm text-brand-gray">
                  <Icon name="check-circle" size="sm" class="text-brand-orange flex-shrink-0" />
                  Moisture source correction
                </li>
                <li class="flex items-center gap-2 text-body-sm text-brand-gray">
                  <Icon name="check-circle" size="sm" class="text-brand-orange flex-shrink-0" />
                  Post-remediation verification
                </li>
              </ul>
            </div>
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>
  
  <!-- Signs of Mold Section -->
  <section class="section bg-white">
    <div class="container">
      <div class="grid lg:grid-cols-2 gap-12 items-center">
        <div class="order-2 lg:order-1">
          <div class="relative">
            <div class="absolute -inset-4 bg-brand-orange/5 rounded-2xl"></div>
            <img 
              src="/images/services/mold/moisture-meter.jpg" 
              alt="Professional mold inspection with moisture meter"
              class="relative rounded-xl shadow-soft-xl w-full"
              loading="lazy"
            />
          </div>
        </div>
        
        <div class="order-1 lg:order-2">
          <h2 class="font-display text-display-lg text-brand-black mb-6">
            Signs You May Have a Mold Problem
          </h2>
          
          <p class="text-body-lg text-brand-gray mb-6">
            Mold often grows in hidden areas before becoming visible. Watch for these warning signs and call for a professional inspection if you notice any:
          </p>
          
          <div class="space-y-4">
            <div class="flex items-start gap-4 p-4 bg-brand-cream-200 rounded-lg">
              <div class="flex-shrink-0 w-10 h-10 rounded-full bg-brand-orange text-white flex items-center justify-center">
                <Icon name="search" size="md" />
              </div>
              <div>
                <h3 class="font-heading font-bold text-brand-black mb-1">Visible Mold Growth</h3>
                <p class="text-body-sm text-brand-gray">Black, green, white, or fuzzy patches on walls, ceilings, floors, or other surfaces—even small spots can indicate larger hidden problems.</p>
              </div>
            </div>
            
            <div class="flex items-start gap-4 p-4 bg-brand-cream-200 rounded-lg">
              <div class="flex-shrink-0 w-10 h-10 rounded-full bg-brand-orange text-white flex items-center justify-center">
                <Icon name="alert-triangle" size="md" />
              </div>
              <div>
                <h3 class="font-heading font-bold text-brand-black mb-1">Musty, Earthy Odors</h3>
                <p class="text-body-sm text-brand-gray">A persistent musty smell, especially in basements, bathrooms, or areas with water exposure, often indicates hidden mold growth.</p>
              </div>
            </div>
            
            <div class="flex items-start gap-4 p-4 bg-brand-cream-200 rounded-lg">
              <div class="flex-shrink-0 w-10 h-10 rounded-full bg-brand-orange text-white flex items-center justify-center">
                <Icon name="droplet" size="md" />
              </div>
              <div>
                <h3 class="font-heading font-bold text-brand-black mb-1">Water Damage History</h3>
                <p class="text-body-sm text-brand-gray">Past leaks, flooding, or water damage—even if dried—create conditions for mold growth within walls and under flooring.</p>
              </div>
            </div>
            
            <div class="flex items-start gap-4 p-4 bg-brand-cream-200 rounded-lg">
              <div class="flex-shrink-0 w-10 h-10 rounded-full bg-brand-orange text-white flex items-center justify-center">
                <Icon name="info" size="md" />
              </div>
              <div>
                <h3 class="font-heading font-bold text-brand-black mb-1">Health Symptoms</h3>
                <p class="text-body-sm text-brand-gray">Unexplained allergies, respiratory issues, or symptoms that improve when away from home may indicate mold exposure.</p>
              </div>
            </div>
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>
  
  <!-- What's Included -->
  <section class="section bg-brand-cream-200">
    <div class="container">
      <div class="text-center max-w-3xl mx-auto mb-12">
        <h2 class="font-display text-display-lg text-brand-black mb-4">
          What's Included in Our Mold Remediation Service
        </h2>
        <p class="text-body-lg text-brand-gray">
          Complete mold elimination from inspection to restoration—handled by certified professionals.
        </p>
      </div>
      
      <div class="grid md:grid-cols-2 lg:grid-cols-3 gap-6">
        {service.features.map((feature) => (
          <div class="bg-white rounded-xl p-6 shadow-soft">
